   Ghandar, Adam; Hua, Zhengchang; Hanai, Masatoshi; Theodoropoulos, Georgios, Southern Univ Sci \& Technol, Dept Comp Sci \& Engn, Shenzhen 518055, Peoples R China.
   Ahmed, Ayyaz; Zulfiqar, Shahid, UET Lahore, Al Khawarizmi Inst Comp Sci, Lahore 39161, Pakistan.},
