   Yang, Huanyu; Yang, Dong, China Acad Transportat Sci, Beijing 100029, Peoples R China.
   Huang, Wei, CCCC Water Transport Planning \& Design Inst Co Ltd, Beijing 100008, Peoples R China.
   Jiang, Ying, Southeast Univ, Sch Transportat, Nanjing 211189, Peoples R China.},
